Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:33.44,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Greater Edo Pool
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:43.07,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time for a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:45.04,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Your lips must have turned purple by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:47.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the water for ten minutes, you stupid kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:48.97,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,What? I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.17,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Leave us alone, lifeguard guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:52.23,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Have it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:55.17,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don't play it safe in the pool, you'll be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:56.78,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come crying to me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:00.44,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,You can't scare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:02.48,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's play tag!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:04.80,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:06.09,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Lifeguard guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:08.29,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,My friend needs help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:10.45,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,His lips started to turn purple,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:11.56,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,but then it spread
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:15.24,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,until his entire body was purple!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:16.24,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:17.30,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:18.42,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, the purple germs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:20.20,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,haven't spread to his glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:22.60,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Find a warm blanket, some warm soup,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:25.48,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,a warm household, and warm glasses at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:27.96,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:31.96,Main01,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,The purple germs will get us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:35.46,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Now you know how scary the pool is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:36.84,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.14,0:02:40.07,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to make sure none of the customers drowned in fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:42.47,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you scaring them away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:45.60,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hasegawa-san, the pool is a death trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:47.48,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,These kids need to experience the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.82,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,of getting water up your nose, the infections,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.45,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,and the embarrassment of leaving dirty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:52.98,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,underwear where everyone can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:55.01,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Once they realize how scary the pool is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:57.78,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,they've earned the right to play in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:00.74,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,They don't need to be scared of turning completely purple!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.64,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously! I finally found a job,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:03.93,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,so don't screw this up for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:04.91,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,No funny business!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:08.40,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Watch over the kids as they enjoy their summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.50,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,and make sure that they make it home safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:12.92,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,That's the job of a lifeguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:13.50,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.88,Main01,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Aye aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:16.88,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get to have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:18.86,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Four Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:20.57,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been playing the straight man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:21.82,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Do your job, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:23.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:26.12,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,They're checking to see if the water is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:28.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be using inception to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:30.69,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,You just want to take a nap, Idicapriot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:33.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:36.12,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of watching kids with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:38.57,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,bodies that are as flat as Ken Watanabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:42.57,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to see girls with some jugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:46.20,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer vacation, so it's mostly kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:48.83,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, momma. Jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:51.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Whoo! You're right! She's got jugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:53.32,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Giant jugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.82,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:57.66,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a drunk terminator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.09,Main01,Seita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.03,Main01,Seita,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:01.97,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.38,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,You know this hot babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:05.59,Main01,Tsukuyo,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.46,Main01,Tsukuyo,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.94,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he was doing fine a moment ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.06,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,but he just died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:13.85,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:18.16,Main01,Tsukuyo,0000,0000,0000,,Hinowa asked me to teach Seita how to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:22.11,Main01,Tsukuyo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I didn't know what to expect from a pool,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.61,Main01,Tsukuyo,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems to be just like Yoshiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:25.36,Main01,Tsukuyo,0000,0000,0000,,Men and women enjoying themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.59,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,without any clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:27.68,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.37,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what this place is for!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:30.69,Main01,Seita,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukuyo-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.99,Main01,Seita,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go down the slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:34.87,Main01,Tsukuyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. First, you learn how to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.29,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.89,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,The slide is too dangerous for someone who can't swim,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:39.13,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,so start with the kiddie pool...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:40.81,Main01,Tsukuyo,0000,0000,0000,,First, you pour this over your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:42.38,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,That would be for an adult pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.72,Main01,Tsukuyo,0000,0000,0000,,Next, you sit down on this stool and spread your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.47,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:49.10,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you teaching him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.86,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a Yoshiwara pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:51.85,Main01,Tsukuyo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:52.47,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.80,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,We're going too fast because of the lotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.94,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Run away, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:12.47,Main01,Seita,0000,0000,0000,,That was awesome, Tsukuyo-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:13.86,Main01,Seita,0000,0000,0000,,Again! Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.87,Main01,Tsukuyo,0000,0000,0000,,One more time and that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.06,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:21.38,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There's a body floating on the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:24.26,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Did someone get hit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:26.84,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,There's been an accident on my watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:33.19,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Elizabeth! The watermelon's nice and cold now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:35.80,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split it open...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:43.36,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,We're losing customers because of those idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.70,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,We have to keep an eye on the kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.64,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and any adults who might teach the kids strange games.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:51.19,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Good, I have an excuse to look around for girls with jugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:53.91,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,The most dangerous adult is standing right next to me, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:55.17,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:57.50,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,An adult in the kiddie pool teaching a kid how to swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.17,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Adults aren't allowed in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.92,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What?! She's got big jugs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.65,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'd call those tasteful cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.63,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,She's wearing a cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:06.92,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's what you meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.43,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:10.03,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,The kid is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.75,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Is she really a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:12.68,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.43,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's taller than the beanpole with cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:17.82,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Kids these days get plenty to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:19.50,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,so they grow vertically.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:21.69,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's Robert De Flato.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.90,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.94,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,That's the body of a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:27.29,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:28.55,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It suddenly got dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:29.32,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:32.83,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Who were you calling Robert De Flato?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:35.27,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,M-My mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.98,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Sylvester Stallone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:38.64,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have an autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.50,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Are you blind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:51.52,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:54.39,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Tasteful cups on a beanpole...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.10,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I didn't want to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.89,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,I hate swimsuits! I hate the pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:03.73,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Kyu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.32,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are you bastards doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:07.94,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to strangle you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:09.12,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:11.99,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We were doing our job as lifeguards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.26,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Zip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.37,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Your noses are bleeding, you pervs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Our noses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:18.70,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We're bleeding everywhere, thanks to you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:20.74,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this is the kiddie pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.21,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Adults aren't allowed in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:23.90,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:26.56,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Kyu-chan can't swim, so she was practicing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:28.87,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kyu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:33.32,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault for forcing you to come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.67,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Kyu-chan looks pretty happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:39.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,She's taking full advantage of the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.79,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:43.44,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,We're turning you in to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:44.70,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,That's the quickest solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.07,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This is all a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.77,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Otae-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:49.09,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:51.20,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I have proof of their crime on tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:53.45,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll arrest them on the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.45,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.66,Main01,Tojo,0000,0000,0000,,Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.51,Main01,Tojo,0000,0000,0000,,I have filmed the evildoings of that cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:00.95,Main01,Tojo,0000,0000,0000,,The stalker is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:02.33,Main01,Tojo,0000,0000,0000,,Our plan is a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.46,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,I was never part of any plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.24,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I did it, Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:08.34,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got a shot of your willy peeking out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:11.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to do with what's going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:14.89,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Blood! Blood's coming from the other pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.65,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,The customers are running away again!
